OL,3,CHearing on transgender prisoners to
OL,4,Cstart in Edinburgh
OL,6,FA legal challenge against the Scottish
OL,7,FGovernment's policy on transgender
OL,8,Fprisoners will commence on Tuesday.
OL,10,FThe judicial review hearing begins at
OL,11,Fthe Court of Session in Edinburgh and
OL,12,Fwill hear from For Women Scotland,
OL,13,Fwhich is opposed to trans women being
OL,14,Fplaced in female-only prisons.
OL,16,FThe group won a Supreme Court case in
OL,17,FApril last year, with judges at the
OL,18,FUK's highest court making clear that
OL,19,Fthe term "woman" in the Equality Act
OL,20,Frefers to a biological woman.
