OL,6,FThe case comes in the wake of the
OL,7,Foutcry over trans rapist Isla Bryson `
OL,8,Fformerly known as Adam Graham ` who
OL,9,Fwas initially sent to Cornton Vale
OL,10,Fwomen's prison in Stirling after being
OL,11,Ffound guilty of sex attacks on two
OL,12,Fwomen in 2023, before then being moved
OL,13,Fto a male prison.
OL,15,FThe Scottish Government's legal
OL,16,Farguments said: "The placement of
OL,17,Fthose prisoners has not given rise to
OL,18,Fany significant operational issue in
OL,19,Fthe prisons in which they have been
OL,20,Fdetained."
