OL,6,FThis guidance, it added, was "informed
OL,7,Fby evidence" that there is both an
OL,8,Fincreased risk of suicide in an
OL,9,Finmate's first three months in
OL,10,Fcustody, and also a "known increased
OL,11,Frisk of suicide for transgender
OL,12,Findividuals".
OL,14,FAs such the legal argument stated that
OL,15,Fthe Scottish Government has a "well-
OL,16,Ffounded concern that being required to
OL,17,Fadopt a policy that a transgender
OL,18,Fprisoner can never be held in a prison
OL,19,Ffor the opposite biological sex could
OL,20,Fgive rise to an unacceptable risk of
OL,21,Fharm".
