OL,6,FBut For Women Scotland previously
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Scottish Government's
OL,8,Fargument makes a great deal about the
OL,9,Fsupposed human right of male prisoners
OL,10,Fto be placed in the female estate but,
OL,11,Fapparently, they have not considered
OL,12,Fthat women also have rights.
OL,14,F"Article 3 protects everyone from
OL,15,Ftorture, inhuman treatment, or
OL,16,Fdegrading punishment, yet women in
OL,17,FScottish prisons are routinely subject
OL,18,Fto boundary violation and physical or
OL,19,Fmental abuse from the men they are
OL,20,Flocked up with.
