OL,6,F"We are pleased, however, that the
OL,7,FEquality and Human Rights Commission
OL,8,Fdoes not agree with the Government's
OL,9,Fposition and that they have intervened
OL,10,Fin support of our case.
OL,12,F"The Scottish Prison Service manage
OL,13,Fmany vulnerable men in prison and 80%
OL,14,Fof transgender prisoners are housed in
OL,15,Fan estate which corresponds to their
OL,16,Fbiological sex."
